title: Saudi CGS, high-powered delegation call on Army Chief, CJCSC
content:
RAWALPINDI, Sep 22 (APP): Chief of General Staff (CGS), Armed Forces of Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, General Fayyadh Bin Hamed Al Ruwaili,alon with a high-powered military delegation, called on Chief of Army Staff, General Syed Asim Munir on Friday.
During the meeting, both sides deliberated upon various areas of mutual interest, bilateral cooperation including defence and security matters, an Inter Services Public Relations (ISPR) news release said.
Earlier, the delegation also met Chairman Joint Chiefs of Staff Committee (CJCSC), General Sahir Shamshad Mirza at Joint Staff Headquarters.
